""SELECT [t].[ParentId], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[Active], COALESCE([x.Products].[Age], 0) AS [Age], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Code], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HomeFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HomeFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[ImageDetail], [x.Products].[ImageThumbs], [x.Products].[Info], COALESCE([x.Products].[LanguageId], 0) AS [LanguageId], [x.Products].[Name], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[New], 0) AS bit) AS [New], [x.Products].[NotePrice], [x.Products].[Parameter], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PriceSale], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[ProductSale], 0) AS bit) AS [ProductSale], [x.Products].[Sale], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeyWords], [x.Products].[SeoTitle], [x.Products].[Size], [x.Products].[SortOrder], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tag], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[Vat], 0) AS bit) AS [Vat], COALESCE([x.Products].[ViewCount], 0) AS [ViewCount], [x.Products].[Warranty]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[ParentId], [x0].[Id]
